All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on Keep a Changelog v1.0.0
(https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/), slightly modified to fit the needs of
this project. This project adheres to Semantic Versioning v2.0.0
(https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

All release dates are formatted as such: MM/DD/YYYY

## v0.2.0-2019.4.21.24c64d - 4/21/2019
### Added
 - Google Analytics tracking of referrals

## v0.2.0-2019.4.21.8dae2e - 4/21/2019
### Added
 - Changelog viewer
 - Roadmap footer link
 - Footer link to feedback Google Form

### Changed
 - Source code footer link now opens in a new tab

## v0.2.0-2019.4.20.d77fb6 - 4/20/2019
### Added
 - UI scaling
 - More UI customization parameters (in Sass)
 - Build scripts to update package.json and add copyright declaration to app.js

## v0.2.0-2019.4.20.a8fbf6 - 4/20/2019
### Fixed
 - School days countdown one day too fast on Saturdays.

## v0.2.0-2019.4.14.62ec2a - 4/14/2019
### Changed
 - School days countdown calculation algorithm

## v0.2.0-2019.4.5.8dbe52 - 4/5/2019
### Added
 - Countdown mode (calendar / school days) toggle button with the appropriate
   icons

## v0.2.0-2019.4.4.227d04 - 4/4/2019
### Added
 - School days countdown to graduation.
